Hibernate: 
    select
        lobby0_.id as id1_5_,
        lobby0_.active as active2_5_,
        lobby0_.code as code3_5_ 
    from
        lobby lobby0_ 
    inner join
        lobby_users users1_ 
            on lobby0_.id=users1_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user2_ 
            on users1_.users_id=user2_.id 
    where
        user2_.id=?
Hibernate: 
    select
        game0_.id as id1_3_,
        game0_.active as active2_3_,
        game0_.creation_date as creation3_3_,
        game0_.ending_date as ending_d4_3_,
        game0_.lobby_id as lobby_id5_3_ 
    from
        game game0_ 
    inner join
        lobby lobby1_ 
            on game0_.lobby_id=lobby1_.id 
    inner join
        lobby_users users2_ 
            on lobby1_.id=users2_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user3_ 
            on users2_.users_id=user3_.id 
    where
        user3_.nickname=? 
        and game0_.active=1

Hibernate: 
    select
        lobby0_.id as id1_5_,
        lobby0_.active as active2_5_,
        lobby0_.code as code3_5_ 
    from
        lobby lobby0_ 
    inner join
        lobby_users users1_ 
            on lobby0_.id=users1_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user2_ 
            on users1_.users_id=user2_.id 
    where
        user2_.id=?
Hibernate: 
    select
        game0_.id as id1_3_,
        game0_.active as active2_3_,
        game0_.creation_date as creation3_3_,
        game0_.ending_date as ending_d4_3_,
        game0_.lobby_id as lobby_id5_3_ 
    from
        game game0_ 
    inner join
        lobby lobby1_ 
            on game0_.lobby_id=lobby1_.id 
    inner join
        lobby_users users2_ 
            on lobby1_.id=users2_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user3_ 
            on users2_.users_id=user3_.id 
    where
        user3_.nickname=? 
        and game0_.active=1

        lobby0_.id as id1_5_,
        lobby0_.active as active2_5_,
        lobby0_.code as code3_5_ 
    from
        lobby lobby0_ 
    inner join
        lobby_users users1_ 
            on lobby0_.id=users1_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user2_ 
            on users1_.users_id=user2_.id 
    where
        user2_.id=?
Hibernate: 
    select
        game0_.id as id1_3_,
        game0_.active as active2_3_,
        game0_.creation_date as creation3_3_,
        game0_.ending_date as ending_d4_3_,
        game0_.lobby_id as lobby_id5_3_ 
    from
        game game0_ 
    inner join
        lobby lobby1_ 
            on game0_.lobby_id=lobby1_.id 
    inner join
        lobby_users users2_ 
            on lobby1_.id=users2_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user3_ 
            on users2_.users_id=user3_.id 
    where
        user3_.nickname=? 
        and game0_.active=1

        game0_.id as id1_3_,
        game0_.active as active2_3_,
        game0_.creation_date as creation3_3_,
        game0_.ending_date as ending_d4_3_,
        game0_.lobby_id as lobby_id5_3_ 
    from
        game game0_ 
    inner join
        lobby lobby1_ 
            on game0_.lobby_id=lobby1_.id 
    inner join
        lobby_users users2_ 
            on lobby1_.id=users2_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user3_ 
            on users2_.users_id=user3_.id 
    where
        user3_.nickname=? 
        and game0_.active=1
Hibernate: 
    select
        round0_.id as id1_7_,
        round0_.game_id as game_id2_7_ 
    from
        round round0_ 
    where
        round0_.game_id=?

        turn0_.round_id=?

            on users1_.users_id=user2_.id 
    where
        user2_.id=?

        game0_.ending_date as ending_d4_3_,
        game0_.lobby_id as lobby_id5_3_ 
    from
        game game0_ 
    inner join
        lobby lobby1_ 
            on game0_.lobby_id=lobby1_.id 
    inner join
        lobby_users users2_ 
            on lobby1_.id=users2_.lobby_id 
    inner join
        user user3_ 
            on users2_.users_id=user3_.id 
    where
        user3_.nickname=? 
        and game0_.active=1
